OL,4,CIndian dowry payments remarkably
OL,5,Cstable, study says
OL,6, Dowry payments in India's villages have
OL,7, been largely stable over the past few
OL,8, decades, a World Bank study has found.
OL,10,FResearchers looked at 40,000 marriages
OL,11,Fthat took place in rural India between
OL,12,F1960 and 2008.
OL,14,FThey found that dowry was paid in 95%
OL,15,Fof the marriages even though it's been
OL,16,Fillegal in India since 1961.
OL,18,FThe practice, often described as a
OL,19,Fsocial evil, continues to thrive and
OL,20,Fleaves women vulnerable to domestic
OL,21,Fviolence and even death.
